@media print {

#tally-widget-button {
  position: fixed !important;
  background-color: #FFFFFF;
  display: none;
  visibility: visible !important;
  opacity: 1 !important;
  color: #0C121D;
  border: 2px solid #0C121D;

  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 14px;

  text-align: center;

  z-index: 999999 !important;

  outline: none;
  touch-action: manipulation;
  pointer-events: auto;
  transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
}
.button-text {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-right: 8px;
}
.button-text::before {
  content: attr(data-text);
}
#tally-widget-popup {
  position: fixed;
  background-color: white;
  display: none;
  border-radius: 12px;

}

  position: absolute;
  top: 10px;
  right: 10px;
  background: none;

  padding: 8px;

  color: #0C121D;
}

  .ab-plugin-wrapper .ab-link-block-item .ab-link {
